======== SAMPLE 1 ========
, the house was in a great need of repair. It stood idle for years.

The house had been abandoned in the twice of the same year. There have been many, many other similar huts, but it seemed to me the better for the same reason. It was in an unoccupied condition, but there was a strong suspicion among burghers that there was a large house down the road, with lots down the Thames that were either too big for the town, or were not suitable for the place. I was a forester for four years and a half, and had grown up in a good household with good friends,
